  </div>
  <h3>rosenhøj <br /> sommer 2023</h3>
  <article>
    <div>
      <h4>rosenhøj glamping</h4>
      <span>available from May - September</span>
    </div>
    <p>Enjoy our beautiful gardens and relax in nature this summer, with our unique urban glamping experience!</p>
    <a href="">read more</a>
  </article>
  <article>
    <div>
      <h4>SUMMER SUPPERCLUB</h4>
      <span>Friday, 30th June - from 19:00</span>
