      <li>Svendborg Jazz Festival<span>23rd - 24th June</span></li>
      <li>Kulinarisk SydFyn<span>24 th - 25th June</span></li>
      <li>Hansted Live<span>27th - 29th July</span></li>
      <li>Dansk Top Festival<span>17th - 19th August</span></li>
    </ul>
    <a href="">book room</a>
